<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.7.0/styles/default.min.css">
<div class="container text-center mt-5">
  <h1 class="mb-5 display-3">Blockly</h1>
  <p>Apprendre à coder ne sera bientôt plus un problème.</p>
  <p>Blockly est un langage de programmation visuel qui facilite l'apprentissage du codage.</p>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5" data-controller="blockly">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div id="blockly" data-blockly-target="container"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
        <div class="card-header">Code Output</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <pre>
            <code class="language-javascript" data-blockly-target="code_output"></code>
          </pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mt-3 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" data-action="click->blockly#runCode" data-blockly-target="runCode">
        Run Code
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
